Package org.scictrl.csshell

Interface Response<C extends AbstractConnector<?>>

All Known Implementing Classes:
ResponseImpl
public interface Response<C extends AbstractConnector<?>>
This interface describes a response to a request. A response to request can be for example a change of value, an error, ...
Author:
igor@scictrl.com
